</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="127" pageNumber="406" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="127.[153,1359,1559,2144]" pageId="127" pageNumber="406">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[153,393,1914,1947]" pageId="127" pageNumber="406">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
One Peruvian Fish-eating Rat was captured in a pitfall trap after heavy rain, suggesting terrestrial displacement can occur during this kind of weather.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
